<li id="mwAas"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Alchemy_and_chemistry_in_medieval_Islam" title="Alchemy and chemistry in medieval Islam" id="mwAaw">Alchemy and chemistry in medieval Islam</a></li>
