rthelot" title="Marcellin Berthelot" id="mwAxo">Marcellin Berthelot</a> at <figure-inline typeof="mw:Transclusion mw:Image" about="#mwt261" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite EB1911","href":"./Template:Cite_EB1911"},"params":{"wstitle":{"wt":"Geber"},"volume":{"wt":"11"},"page":{"wt":"545"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAxs"><span id="mwAxw"><img alt="Wikisource" resource="./File:Wikisource-logo.svg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4c/Wikisource-logo.svg/12px-Wikisource-logo.svg.png" data-file-width="410" data-file-height="430" data-file-type="drawing" height="13" width="12" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4c/Wikisource-logo.svg/24px-Wikisource-logo.svg.png 2x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4c/Wikisource-logo.svg/18px-Wikisource-logo.svg.png 1.5x" id="mwAx0"/></span></figure-inline><span typeof="mw:Entity" about="#mwt261" id="mwAx4"> </span><cite class="citation encyclopaedia" about="#mwt261" id="mwAx8">Chisholm, Hugh, ed. (1911). <span class="cs1-ws-icon" title="Wikisource:1911 Encyclopædia Britannica/Geber" id="mwAyA"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/1911_Encyclop%C3%A6dia_Britannica/Geber" id="mwAyE">"Geber"<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwAyI"> </span></a></span>. <i id="mwAyM"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Encyclopædia_Britannica_Eleventh_Edition" title="Encyclopædia Britannica Eleventh Edition" id="mwAyQ">Encyclopædia Britannica</a></i>. <b id="mwAyU">11</b> (11th ed.). Cambridge University Press. p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwAyY"> </span>545.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=Geber&amp;rft.btitle=Encyclop%C3%A6dia+Britannica&amp;rft.pages=545&amp;rft.edition=11th&amp;rft.pub=Cambridge+University+Press&amp;rft.date=1911&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJabir+ibn+Hayyan" class="Z3988" about="#mwt261" id="mwAyc"></span><link rel="mw-deduplica